â˜¸ï¸ Kubernetes â€” Container Orchestration Platform
ğŸ”¹ What Kubernetes Does:
Once you have many containers running (using Docker or other runtimes), Kubernetes helps to:
Deploy containers to multiple servers
Scale them up/down automatically
Load balance traffic between them
Restart crashed containers
Roll out updates safely

Manage networking, storage, secrets, and configs

ğŸ”¹ Core Components:
